<center>
<h1>Vijay</h1>
</center>
<hr>
<p>
    Actor Vijay, whose full name is Joseph Vijay Chandrasekhar, is a leading star in the Tamil film industry and one of the most influential actors in South Indian cinema. Fondly known as "Thalapathy" by his fans, Vijay began his acting career in the early 1990s and rose to fame with a mix of romantic, dramatic, and action-packed films. 
    His breakthrough came with the film *Ghilli* in 2004, and since then, he has delivered numerous blockbusters like *Thuppakki*, *Mersal*, *Bigil*, and *Master*.
     Known for his stylish screen presence, exceptional dancing skills, and strong connection with the masses, Vijay commands a massive fan following worldwide. 
     Apart from acting, he is also involved in social work through his fan association, Vijay Makkal Iyakkam, which carries out welfare activities across Tamil Nadu. 
     In 2024, Vijay officially announced his entry into politics by launching his own party, Tamizhaga Vetri Kazhagam, aiming to bring change in the stateâ€™s political landscape. Despite being a private individual off-screen, his on-screen persona and growing political aspirations continue to capture the public's imagination.

